## Polyploid speciation

<#b2cols>

- Divergence can also occur when mutation causes genetic incompatibility
    - <#gloss autopolyploid> (same-species) speciation:
chromosome doubling within one mate
	- <#gloss allopolyploid> (other-species) speciation:
hybridization + chromosome doubling
- common in plants  
(cellular mechanisms, hybridization, self-fertilization)

